Welcome to Stanly Community College

Page path
  • Home

  • Welcome to Moodle at Stanly Community College!

    To access your courses, log-in using the same username and password that you use for your student Gmail account and Web Advisor.

    After logging-in, be sure to click on "Courses" in the Navigation block to the left to view and access your current list of courses. Click on the icons below for more information about Stanly Community College's student services.

  •


(When you are ready to log out Click Here.)

Don't Get Dropped!!

Students must, for each online class:

  • log in on the first day of class.
    • You will have access by 9:00am on the first day of your class.
    • Please double check the course start date as some courses start later than others.
  • submit the first activity on or before its due date 

Students not meeting this mandate will be dropped.
